Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I cannot help\Nbut feel responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,True, my story is\Nan inspiring one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not really what you'd\Ncall an adventurous dresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.07,0:01:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,--More of a plain Jane.\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Secret Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello! Welcome to Secret Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:02:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanna come\Nout and play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, hey! You wanna\Ncome out and play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, hey! Wanna come out play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, hey!\NWanna come out and play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Haven't you ever\Nheard of a doorbell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I brought some cards.\NYou wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like a billion\Ndegrees outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:36.57,Main,,0,0,0,,and you walked over here\Nto play a card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why not?\NWe'll play Go Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NThat's the lamest game ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:42.70,Main,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna hang out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,let's at least\Ngo somewhere cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NAh! Blessed air conditioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Amen, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Have you done\Nthe homework we got
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,for summer break yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYeah, most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take a wild guess\Nand say that you haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured I could just copy\Nyours when you were done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:10.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Do your own work,\Nyou lazy mooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,No fair! How 'bout you, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIs she sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NSure looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NUm, is your face okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep your filthy\Nhands off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughs awkwardly]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't mind us. Just a little\Njoke between girlfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs awkwardly]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] So... What's up\Nwith you, sleeping beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry; it's not\Nthat I wasn't having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,The cool air is so relaxing, I\Nguess I dozed off for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You getting sick?\NYou aren't usually this tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. I've just\Nbeen working a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Still at the cake place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,With the weirdly\Nyoung-looking maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you were going\Nto pick up extra shifts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.55,Main,,0,0,0,,during the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd probably be there now if\Nit wasn't closed for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think maybe you're\Nworking yourself too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Most folks lie down to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,No. I'm fine.\NDon't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhoa! That looks so painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Not to mention gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NYou fell asleep at the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.24,Main,,0,0,0,,That's both sad and amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can work in\Nthe front of the shop today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Your face might scare\Noff the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on.\NIt's not really that bad, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It happened 'cause\Nshe's working too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI gasps]\NThis is a travesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you let\NMiss Yoko get injured?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And on her forehead!\NHer lovely face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Her perfect\Naristocratic visage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What if it leaves a scar?\NHave you thought about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You must see a doctor\Nat once, Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one who needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,But I think he needs a\Ndifferent kind of doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NAh! The work force is no place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,for a delicate flower like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You're too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's time to stop\Ncoddling Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] This is your\Nfault, devil-woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.49,Main,,0,0,0,,We've known each other for\Na long time, but work is work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't give you\Nspecial treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't asked\Nfor any, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NI'm glad you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I would appreciate it if\Nyou'd go into the back room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I prefer my employees\Nto be well rested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I cannot help\Nbut feel responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,True, my story\Nis an inspiring one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:45.22,Main,,0,0,0,,A humble servant turned\Nsuccessful business tycoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,But not everybody has\Nthe strength of character
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,to travel the path I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I blame myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,In seeking to emulate me,\Nyou came to harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you hit your head\Non something, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Your boss said to rest,\Nso off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.44,Main,,0,0,0,,No arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What about the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to be\Nshort-handed without her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NWhat do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.83,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can run\Nthis place all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.58,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's that big a deal,\Nwhy'd you give Yoko the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:17.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You could take Yoko's\Nplace for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's not like you've\Ngot anything better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Says the girl who\Nwanted to play Go Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not volunteer yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.39,Main,,0,0,0,,We're short on time,\Nso let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,But those clothes have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHey! Stop! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Nobody said anything\Nabout maid cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NI thought it would be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not! I wanna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Why can't I just wear\Nthe same thing Yoko does?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.78,Main,,0,0,0,,That is so not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you finished\Nchanging, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.37,Main,,0,0,0,,We should really\Nbe getting to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] This might be worth\Nthe humiliation after all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.33,Main,,0,0,0,,if I get to see Futaba\Nin these stupid clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ready to go, boss!\N--[HAYAMA] Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NMy clothes didn't fit her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,so we had to go\Nwith something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat didn't fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Well, the bust\Nand hip areas were snug.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying she's got\Na killer body or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I've always been a bit\Non the smaller side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll fill\Nout though, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWho said I was worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NOops. I hit a nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm kind of\Na special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't grown\Nsince junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, it was\Nmore like elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Saying that I have the\Nbody of a 10-year-old
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,isn't reassuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Look on the bright side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,If you stop growing, you won't\Nhave to diet when you get older.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we just drop it already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Secret Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Where's the usual girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Does she have the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.\NWe're filling in for her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,So many young\Ngirls working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet it makes the\Njob more fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Definitely!\NSo what can we get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything in particular\Nyou'd recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything's good, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to say, though, I\Nespecially like this roll cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's simple and light,\Nmade from an airy sponge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,wrapped around\Nluscious buttercream
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,and infused with the just the\Nright amount of green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Then of course,\Nthere's the gateau chocolat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Its refined sweetness pairs\Nperfectly with a cup
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,of dark coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,The chocolate is sinfully rich,\Nwith just a hint of bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Finally, the strawberry\Nmousse cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.29,Main,,0,0,0,,This confection pairs the tangy\Nsweetness of strawberries
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,with the lush richness of cream,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,creating an explosion of flavor\Nthat will leave you gasping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You make it so hard to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have\Nto take all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll box 'em up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow. That was hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,She makes it sound like\Na smutty romance novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.68,Main,,0,0,0,,So... you're up next, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] It's not like I'm\Nthreatened by Futaba,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.23,Main,,0,0,0,,but I don't want Sonobe\Nto think I can't do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Welco--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Secret Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Which of our mouthwatering\Ncakes can I get for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! You really are\Ndressed up like a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at you! You're adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:59.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I know, right?\NIsn't it perfect on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You're looking pretty\Nchic today, yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I told her you were cosplaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:10.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You make a great maid, Teru.\NKeep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's some candy\Nto keep you going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, what kind of candy is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:26.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] It was very nice\Nof you to come and visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NShe knew just by looking at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Vampires have\Nheightened senses, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NOh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can help bake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make yummy desserts\Nwith a healthy twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be perfect!\NWhat d'you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.67,Main,,0,0,0,,This is our new gelée.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Its combination of\Nvitamin C-packed fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,and collagen make it\Ngreat for your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to come up\Nwith a name for it yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can help me\Nchoose something appealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NI'm at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Not sure how\Nto make it sound appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NI know! Gelée de Pork!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NGelée de Pork?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.15,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds disgusting, Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it is\Nscientifically accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean 'cause collagen\Ncomes from pig skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:13.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, really? I thought it\Nhad a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I think I'll\Njust name it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,--[door opens]\N--[YU] Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard you're working here.\NIs it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's that?\NOh, I recognize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NI know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was the\NNishikawas' maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Young Master Takezono.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you people please\Nkeep it down out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko will never get her\Nrest with all this commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Well aren't you\Na cute little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you're\Nhere to see Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I just want to\Nmake sure she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,And, you know, stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThat's very sweet of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You always were a nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,And adorable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at your cute\Nlittle bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I see that your birthmarks\Nhave already faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stay outta my pants, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:10:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You freakin' weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you\Nused to be Yoko's maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't let her work in\Na creepy shop like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gross and you're\Nold and I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.13,Main,,0,0,0,,So there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NSweetie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hush! That's not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Good little boys\Ndon't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It would hurt your\Nfeelings if somebody said
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,mean things like that\Nto you, right? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NYes. It would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] He's really got a\Nthing for older women!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I think there's\Na sweet little boy here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.27,Main,,0,0,0,,who just earned himself\Na yummy little treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles]\NHere, candy, just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I can't wait to try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:38.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, HAYAMA groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I made this for Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll help her\Nrecover her strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NUgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NUgh! I think I'm gonna vomit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,My eyes are burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she licensed\Nfor this kinda thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I think we may all\Nneed some hazmat suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yoko!\NI brought some lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NNo, no, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama! Wanna hang out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:12.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, Nishiyama,\NNishiyama, Nishiyama--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Could you be any\Nmore obnoxious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Step away from the doorbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] C'mon, c'mon!\NLet's get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:22.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Here! It's called Secret Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Their new gelée is\Nsupposed to be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,There were flyers\Nfor it all over school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NI can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really trying to\Nsave money right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NHuh? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.26,Main,,0,0,0,,A camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NWhat for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,To take pictures\Nof my sweet baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have the\Nright equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd\Ngiven up on that by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll make so many\Nmemories this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to capture them all.\NYou know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,So which of these\Nlooks good to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NShe's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER 5B]\NGreat, thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and two of these\Ngelées, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure! Two Gelée de Pork,\Ncoming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba, two pigs,\Nand make it snappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Right! Two pigs, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, Gelée de Pork\Nis really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:19.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It's going quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:21.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Please stop.\NThat's not its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe, we need\Nmore Gelée de Pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,We're all sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:26.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Gelée de Pork is a hit!\NI'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everybody seems\Nto like Gelée de Pork!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:32.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, 'cause Gelée\Nde Pork is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:34.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you seem to\Nhave bounced back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,really quickly there, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:41.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! I think it's because\Nof the food Kou brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I don't know what\Nher secret ingredient is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I've felt strangely\Nenergetic since I ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't sleep at all last\Nnight, and look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You look kinda crazy,\Nto be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:53.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Well, at least\Nshe's got energy now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for shopping with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! They're delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA whining]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:03.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Look! Isn't that Hayama\Nand her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Secret Garden!\NHow are you girls today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you didn't come\Nfor the new gelée,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.64,Main,,0,0,0,,because we just sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NThat's exactly what we wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] Well, maybe\Nwe should just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:17.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Oh, are these ladies\Nacquaintances of yours, Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we all go\Nto the same school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,This is quite a surprise;\NI had no idea you worked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] They're both smiling,\Nso why does it feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,they're about to\Nstab each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Look at that outfit!\NYou're dressed like a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,So is it like a cosplay thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, lemme try!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.51,Main,,0,0,0,,"Here, master.\NI've brought your cake."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:50.22,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a uniform,\Nand therefore not cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] Come on!\NIt's totally cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:53.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NRead my lips, Kondo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NStop! Don't poke the bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But I saw something\Nlike this on TV before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don't work here.\NI'm just helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe needed a\Ncouple of extra servers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,so we volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.70,Main,,0,0,0,,They're lifesavers, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we\Nwould do without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,That's nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I'm so glad\Nto have Hayama's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,She's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,The customers\Nabsolutely adore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:19.21,Main,,0,0,0,,She works quickly\Nand efficiently
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,and can think on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I've\Never met anyone her age
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,who's that competent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, you're too kind. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! Working the\Ncounter at a cake shop
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,is something anyone could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not exactly\Nrocket science, now is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess it must\Nbe easy to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.60,Main,,0,0,0,,when you've never\Ndone it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,And I don't know if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got so much\Npride to swallow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you might\Nactually choke on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm not cut out for a job\Nin customer service like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,since I'm not brave enough\Nwear an outfit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.79,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not really what you'd\Ncall an adventurous dresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,More of a plain Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever know\Nwhen to shut your mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And stop acting like an expert!\NIt's been what, a day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:01.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] That sort of\Nemotional outburst is why
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think you\Ncould handle this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] There's an\Neasy way to settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Unless you're too chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NWhoops, I'm sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:15.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess my hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It slipped five times?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] Can't you find another\Nway to amuse yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:21.27,Main,,0,0,0,,besides toying with people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.\NMy motives were pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Is everyone here crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] No matter what I do,\NI can't get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:34.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to your\Nhouse and stuff our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Hold on!\NI have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NGo ahead. Take 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Leftovers from a special\Norder I made myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,All-natural, organic pet treats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,A gift for your kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It might be the\Nbest bakery in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] I can't believe\NHayama works there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, isn't that crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[KITTEN meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You like the treats, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[KITTEN meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't\Nhave any more for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The shop isn't open yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Does this mean you've\Ndecided to come work for me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhat? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling you\Nmight have a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\Neverything's ready for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:49.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NOh, god. What am I wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember to smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the most\Nimportant part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this\Nis my life right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama has a great smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, it just brightens\Nup the whole room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't ask you to match that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.29,Main,,0,0,0,,but you could be\Na little friendlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,If Hayama can do it,\Nthen so can I!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:11.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello! Welcome\Nto Secret Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why are you\Ntaking pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Your "welcome" doesn't\Nsound very welcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something very forced\Nand unnatural about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Hayama told me\Nyou have a kitty at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,According to her, you're\Nextraordinarily fond of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not imagine\Nyourself playing with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That should help\Nyou look happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NPlaying with my kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.12,Main,,0,0,0,,That would probably\Njust scare people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, let me see!\NWhat did I look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NI'm sorry! Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NAw! This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine, don't worry.\NThere's no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks! The ribbon's\Na little tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it your first day here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You must love wearing\Nsuch a cute uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I can see through\Nthat tough exterior
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,of yours, Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:16.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You pretended not to like it,\Nbut that was an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:20.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You felt special getting dressed\Nup in your sweet little outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice! Keep up the\Ngood work, Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] Thanks!\NThat kinda came outta nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] I'll take it,\Nthough. Praise is praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.88,Main,,0,0,0,,After all,\Nanything Hayama can do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,should be simple\Nenough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! I am strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Secret Ga--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NUh, is that who I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NOh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I should've seen this coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course they'd drop by.\NThey work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.03,Main,,0,0,0,,And now they've\Nall seen me in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it too late to duck\Nbehind the counter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.08,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll take one dozen\Nfinanciers, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhy's she being nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Sonobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why you\Nsuddenly gave me the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you replacing\Nme or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, Nishiyama has a\Nmassive inferiority complex,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,and I thought I might be able\Nto help her out with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhat? That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you just whip\Nthat up last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth is I'd\Noriginally designed it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,with Miss Yoko in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NMe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I decided it would be\Ntoo tight in the chest area
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,for her to wear, but it was\Nthe perfect size for Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER 5D]\NExcuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NMan, this place is packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NHere, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It's difficult for anyone\Nuntil you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's a strawberry\Nmousse, a roll cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,and a gateau chocolat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I'm so sorry.\NThank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of\Nyou soon, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I think you're really\Ngonna love this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's new and super tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.99,Main,,0,0,0,,High school girls bonding,\Nsmiling, making nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm getting younger\Nby the second!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NI'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:27.91,Main,,0,0,0,,We're all sold out\Nof Gelée de Pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:31.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But maybe you'd like to try this\Ngreen tea roll cake instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Great! You'll love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Man, I'm not used\Nto working that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NOh, well. It was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I got these kitty treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:55.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a small world, huh?\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:00.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] I'm just looking\Naround for a good camera
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,so I can take better--[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:04.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you printing those out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I thought they'd\Nmake nice mementos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:08.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't need them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean you don't\Nneed mementos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,because you're going\Nto keep working for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Just delete those\Nfrom your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:18.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean it! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThis is Shino...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:51.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] ...and Selina's\Nnext episode preview!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.64,0:23:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Nishiyama,\Nyou're a capable woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,so I leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:55.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhat? Well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time:\N"Veggies, Meat, Meat, Meat,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Meat, Meat, Meat and Fish."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Please watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You made me do it,\Nso what's with that reaction?
